{"tid":1631881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線做野前諗諗先唔好衝動","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:21:39.000Z","uid":277855,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ee1c7b409605ccae7d824cb32cc6ebf06f4ad351","tid":1631881,"uid":277855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"今日九龍塘 有架私家車 司機拎部電話出黎 我屌你 你班友拎個錘仔出黎打爛人地個銀幕？唔會問清楚先架 唔撚識睇情況架 屌你老母！入面一家大細 兩個細佬系到 我屌你老母 嚇親細佬架 細佬無辜架 就算系藍絲都唔應該咁啦 細佬無辜架！做野用下腦啦 搞撚到幾個勇武要道歉 仲拎晒身上所有錢賠返比司機！因為你一個無腦行為！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最重要仲要個司機系支持勇武做野！<span style=\"color: red;\"></span></span>"},{"pid":"ed94b5dd63944de56678f9aee28b9a698359df1d","tid":1631881,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"b2bef085d5cd844b14aacb22681234daa9194f41","tid":1631881,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:31:12.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"3261c9ffcf998dcf7d25c9a87e636c531a0f26cb","tid":1631881,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"如果係真<br />\n前線唔該冷靜少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823fe70380e239121d353a5fae788d7834ee789d","tid":1631881,"uid":127379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nvdq2Uf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvdq2Uf.jpg&h=933290b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f392e6bdb34d4fcfac484b6ff2b6697875d8f4f","tid":1631881,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:34:04.000Z","msg":"講左4個月 be humble <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a821e3ae8835f5219c1e884ff1504a71606cdf","tid":1631881,"uid":324892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c8218d0772b92527b8b0911d43eb245f9ac81ed","tid":1631881,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"其實已經開左好多Post係咁屌勇武，留番D力去做文宣啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不推不回覆。</span></span>"},{"pid":"938b3745890bb21d4b2198c5d7c974fea1c175aa","tid":1631881,"uid":277855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3261c9ffcf998dcf7d25c9a